  "title": "KYC",
  "description": "<p>Job Description:<br />We are seeking an experienced professional to join our team as an Onboarding & Client Lifecycle Specialist. In this role, you will:</p><ul><li>Perform onboarding processes including document review and account set-up.</li><li>Ensure adherence to regulations, guidelines, standards, and policies.</li><li>Maintain in-depth awareness of potential legislative and policy breaches and act proactively to prevent their occurrence.</li><li>Provide advisory and hotline support to internal clients. Business partners include, but are not limited to, Operations, Legal & Compliance, Business Risk Management, and Project teams.</li><li>Engage in process improvement projects to streamline and automate document review and static data update processes.</li></ul><p><strong>You are:</strong><br />Self-starter with ability to work independently and minimal supervision.</p><p><p>Methodical, concise, and accurate with strong attention to detail.</p></p><p><p>Excellent communication skills; comfortable engaging with multiple stakeholders.</p></p><p><p>Effective team player with professional and positive attitude.</p></p><p><p>Able to work under pressure and meet strict deadlines; strong task prioritization skills.</p></p><p><p>Skilled in improving processes and enhancing workflows.</p></p><p><p>Innovative with data and adaptable to a changing business environment.</p></p><p>This position is open to all who are fulfilling aforesaid requirements</p>",
